div2.p:
Similar design, probably a contemporary counterfeit. Same legends, but no real similarity to the normal piece. Discovery piece is New York Coin & Stamp, June 1890 ( Parmelee ), 450;
                       NNC; Fuld (1967); Picker in only Fair condition. Another specimen was discovered by
                           Boyd , now Ford in extremely fine condition.

